body:
[changelog](https://curl.haxx.se/changes.html#7_53_1)

**REMEMBER**: these "releases" on github are only the entire source code repo at the time of the tag put into a compressed file, they are not identical to the [officially blessed release tarballs](https://curl.haxx.se/download.html) found on the web site. The release tarballs get a bunch of files included that are generated in the release process, and these github "releases" do not.

name: curl 7.50.3
body:
[changelog](https://curl.haxx.se/changes.html#7_50_3)

The official **real** releases are provided at [curl.haxx.se](https://curl.haxx.se/download.html) - what you find here at github are archived versions of the source tree at the time the release tag was made.
The release tarballs are not hosted on github. See https://curl.haxx.se/download.html
